<p local-id=3D"d3acf8c4-8be8-4a5c-8370-31a53d8bc63c"></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"bc74e154-059e-4045-a43d-4583de265a0d">
<td data-local-id=3D"c9fda3ec-c3ea-4247-9f87-6dddfcf26dbc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"156fcf08-3232-413f-8444-eccc64469a00"><strong>Final Approver=
</strong> (Tag the approver)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7fb94a44-eb4c-4047-bcfa-de3a7fdce9ac" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5c838f41-26fb-434b-8d65-9cab50aa1c6e"></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"cc1dff3f-97cd-4699-8820-d0da69eb3992"></p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p local-id=3D"4759f372-11d0-4e7e-9ae2-e8105ce0d57c">In November 2025, the =
AEON team made a notable pivot in our approach for the SRE agent. The pivot=
 is captured in <a href=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki/x/aIC9IQE" r=
el=3D"nofollow">this IDD</a> and several CDDs and DACIs have been spun up t=
o capture the updated direction.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"8afe6850-4c93-499a-b5b9-543465468022" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-S=
REAgentCDD-Context/ProblemStatement">Context / Problem Statement</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b70684e0-3396-4edb-9214-493893083927">There has long been a =
desire to enable using New Relic data to proactively speed up detection and=
 resolution of problems, improve code quality, and make deployment cycles m=
ore robust and streamlined.</p>
<p local-id=3D"60f7a025-40b0-4b89-b70d-f446f664a004">We have produced a myr=
iad of AI-empowered features via New Relic AI since 2023. Most of these fea=
tures have been Directed Acyclic Graph (DAG) workflows starting from a chat=
 experience wherein a user types a message and an LLM provides routing base=
d on most likely tools to fit the user=E2=80=99s request. Although these ca=
pabilities have been able to empower new detection integrations such as our=
 <a href=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki/x/9oAx5Q" rel=3D"nofollow">=
Agentic Integrations in GitHub Copilot</a> from the end of 2024, the capabi=
lities fall short in more elaborate problem spaces.</p>
<p local-id=3D"654257c6f768"></p>
<p local-id=3D"1b2dfecd7ec7">In order to provide a more robust solution to =
proactive detection and site reliability this team has been set upon the go=
al of building an SRE agent tasked to address the following domains:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d8139c13-5281-44a0-bbbd-5233683019eb">
<li local-id=3D"bea71244-d291-4d9a-9ffa-f4ee7ef6c29e">
<p local-id=3D"f7c528c6-7f1e-44e4-bf68-acb663f479af">Alert Triage: "I was p=
aged for entity X. Is this alert concerning?"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58358790-ba37-4fe8-bcce-79e455a26ecc">
<p local-id=3D"11b218ce-4d47-4cd4-9d7f-8ff8f4a65a4c">Entity Health: "How is=
 service X doing?"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a384c252-351f-4347-9594-73ba2ac5e91d">
<p local-id=3D"0e76e4bd-e5ef-4e0e-b59a-aee90ae6d4ca">Change Intelligence: "=
Is the last deployment for service X stable and healthy?"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d3a4582f-541c-4bd5-b7a9-6564afff9511">
<p local-id=3D"bf50a982-0e06-46fd-8ce5-f17e667fbf4f">Incident Analysis: "En=
tity X is down. What caused this outage?"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2a152262-68be-440b-81c0-68a866f1a4a2">
<p local-id=3D"65694e99-5793-4a26-b54e-2796190c1480">Remediation: "The late=
st deployment is awful. What can you do to address this issue?"</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d7ac5d03-da0d-4879-883d-737d5cd02015"></p>
<p local-id=3D"2d87465c-1325-43f3-bc94-b6e90b89c591">Additional reading:</p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"833e1a9f-59c9-4e6a-ba87-8c576ead4e69">
<li local-id=3D"beafdfc7-edcb-4bec-921f-704521693799">
<p local-id=3D"df08bd70-f866-4934-a446-62481c3d7880"><a class=3D"external-l=
ink" href=3D"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1clNP1u3mH3AngkQpY3ue0PCc1Z=
YnXuWUIi8QutxoZUw/edit?usp=3Dsharing" rel=3D"nofollow">Steel thread documen=
tation</a></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3e3320fa0a51"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"fa272314-5932-430b-baa7-a068bfac19de" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-S=
REAgentCDD-Design">Design</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a69d2289-e85c-40ab-adf4-b325d9455f7d">The AEON team shall bu=
ild out a myriad of SRE-oriented MCP tools and a service that will orchestr=
ate an agent through a workflow in a sort of controlled non-determinism.</p=
><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confl=
uence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-c=
enter" alt=3D"image-20260220-212727.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=
=3D"234077ef8d05f26a1f99b0b6ae9f0887c51929d3d2470610f29a24c9c39af0e2" data-=
image-src=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/42834=
01991/image-20260220-212727.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D17716228=
52010&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"921" data-width=3D"=
2023" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"520608=
1546" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attac=
hment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260220-212727.png" dat=
a-base-url=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-con=
tent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"4283401991" da=
ta-linked-resource-container-version=3D"44" data-media-id=3D"3698c61d-017b-=
43a2-8206-0517da2b609b" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"213"></span>
<p local-id=3D"395a1f382e79"></p>
<p local-id=3D"027de9d9c48b"></p>
<p local-id=3D"cd8f7811-ea0f-4c18-855a-959facffdfa1">Links</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2da5c97c-2590-4c95-85d1-7c0f7b332ebc">
<li local-id=3D"996c9048-b09f-4a54-8de6-940ebdd766d7">
<p local-id=3D"70580f6d-a7f2-48c9-b88f-b6227cdf9221"><a class=3D"external-l=
ink" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/Alerting/sre-agent-mcp-server" rel=
=3D"nofollow"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"576cf9c3-46=
7a-4ca4-9eb1-5e2c14512c03">Source code for SRE MCP server</span></a></p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"2a304ff5-e145-439d-af35-ddba4cc5e33b">
<p local-id=3D"b01b8597-211a-472d-9595-7f5eb4c767a8"><a class=3D"external-l=
ink" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/Alerting/sre-orchestration-service"=
 rel=3D"nofollow"><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"576cf9c=
3-467a-4ca4-9eb1-5e2c14512c03">Source code for SRE orchestration service</s=
pan></a></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"899af42ffd46"></p>
<h3 local-id=3D"97cad219f79f" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-Proposed/Lead=
ingSolution">Proposed / Leading Solution</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"7da0c3d8804b">
<li local-id=3D"4451edad1c54">
<p local-id=3D"f4f754dfde1b">NGEP entities are created to manage the detail=
s and onboarding status of the SRE agent</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a4d2bbb6b234">
<li local-id=3D"82d7b121dbd4">
<p local-id=3D"72ec5a4b52e7">AiAgentEntity is created in the New Relic orga=
nization to handle internal details such as discovery path for SRE orchestr=
ation service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"23e1879a5ffc">
<p local-id=3D"6fb945466983">NrAiAgentEntity will be created in the custome=
r organization</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"57dc5e1c7fd8">
<p local-id=3D"577489bb34a0">NRAI Synapse acts as a service proxy for all i=
nteractions with SRE agent</p>
<ul local-id=3D"30ac573e750f">
<li local-id=3D"5f003f1b4565">
<p local-id=3D"bfa2e053f321">AiAgentEntity is referenced to direct requests=
 to SRE orchestration service</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"e84d0fbd1fb1">
<p local-id=3D"f9a9443a0b2e">SRE orchestration service responds asynchronou=
sly by emitting AG UI events</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ffbc7fb8851b">
<p local-id=3D"fff5c9d05b60">NRAI Synapse stores the response from the SRE =
agent in the Collaboration comments database to support conversational memo=
ry</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9e1862e40685">
<p local-id=3D"5127f41d457b">NRAI Synapse handles provisioning and supplyin=
g of system identity access tokens for interactions with SRE agent.</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"de1ab54734a5">
<p local-id=3D"c038a05165ad">SRE orchestration service implements a =E2=80=
=9Ccontrolled non-determinism=E2=80=9D approach to agentic execution wherei=
n a plan is generated, executed, and then an output is synthesized.</p></li=
>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"image-20260223-170257.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy"=
 src=3D"b417ca519bab177d76e94ce2a2fccf42a34134874df946f2884125e9a50480e3" d=
ata-image-src=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/4=
283401991/image-20260223-170257.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1771=
866181105&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"664" data-width=
=3D"1590" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"52=
10767394" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"a=
ttachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260223-170257.png"=
 data-base-url=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource=
-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"4283401991=
" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"44" data-media-id=3D"5bddaa11-d=
9ed-4b70-8e40-0dfcdd191fff" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"195"></span>
<h4 local-id=3D"d2423baf0036" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-Phasesofexecu=
tion">Phases of execution</h4>
<h5 local-id=3D"cab974ce2efd" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-PlanningPhase=
">Planning Phase</h5>
<ul local-id=3D"c3f65a34-af7a-4ea9-8004-148f012300ad">
<li local-id=3D"41eb3eaf-1002-430b-a431-232817be7f85">
<p local-id=3D"7dd9d39ac500">LLM generates an investigation plan based on u=
ser request and available context</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"151f8416-a011-4ace-a132-14485d61c436">
<p local-id=3D"98328ccea272">Plan is validated against allowed tool set and=
 execution constraints</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8bd2f10b-ef20-41b9-8aa7-0781fca103fe">
<p local-id=3D"052869de7780">Pre-approved plans can bypass generation for k=
nown patterns</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ab069909b07f">
<li local-id=3D"0a2af2610199">
<p local-id=3D"1e82e6bee797"><a href=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki=
/spaces/AppInt/pages/5075140637/LangGraph+Router+for+SRE+Agent+Plan+Selecti=
on" data-linked-resource-id=3D"5075140637" data-linked-resource-version=3D"=
7" data-linked-resource-type=3D"page">CDD</a> - Feature started development=
 behind feature flag</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<h5 local-id=3D"099ea4aae58a" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-ExecutionPhas=
e">Execution Phase</h5>
<ul local-id=3D"c13900a1-7a62-4fce-b3e5-83c7a82e0536">
<li local-id=3D"dcd6ab42-f280-4a49-ac14-d18c71643493">
<p local-id=3D"7a34752a02e5">Each plan step executes within defined boundar=
ies</p></li>
</ul>
<h5 local-id=3D"c800c914eb27" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-SynthesisPhas=
e">Synthesis Phase</h5>
<ul local-id=3D"97df4436-1d9b-44b7-ba43-f8e893e9a6b9">
<li local-id=3D"2e6a3b9c-0e6f-4ca3-ac8a-e3931ebe1eca">
<p local-id=3D"db8cf0a47042">Results from executed steps are consolidated i=
nto a coherent response</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c5085cccfccf"></p>
<h4 local-id=3D"41c050d842df" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-Pros">Pros</h=
4>
<ul local-id=3D"b3261cdb2352">
<li local-id=3D"1d5fd0b8e438">
<p local-id=3D"32c0c7e1d6f5">Full control over plan generation, execution b=
oundaries, and error handling.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"560d49ddb32d">
<li local-id=3D"b59f1055f6fd">
<p local-id=3D"70751c1891f8">E.g. - we can implement circuit breakers, toke=
n budgets, and retry strategies without depending on external platform time=
lines.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"07d351a535bd">
<p local-id=3D"1b0c942e8a3c">We can tune orchestration per domain; Not lock=
ed into one-size-fits-all constraints.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a7c220b05311">
<li local-id=3D"9775540816ea">
<p local-id=3D"3e304feba8c8">E.g. - Alert Triage vs. Remediation may need d=
ifferent execution patterns.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"2665aa09d5a9">
<p local-id=3D"cf978c4ffd0b">Access to feature flagged rollouts at multiple=
 layers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94f705fefe4f">
<p local-id=3D"b1465e02581e">Access to custom instrumentation/observability=
</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2d7d0d8b983f"></p>
<h4 local-id=3D"521b73e0c1b0" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-Cons">Cons</h=
4>
<ul local-id=3D"5d4841b8110d">
<li local-id=3D"ec99645e50e7">
<p local-id=3D"f0a100669f30">More expensive to run; This solution will requ=
ire more engineers to build and run than an approach simply generating prom=
pts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e6ef15417d8">
<p local-id=3D"99f29fe0ac63">Some capabilities may overlap with the Agentic=
 Platform as both sides mature</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1dbc90f29278">
<p local-id=3D"7f8724fadc24">Complex plans with larger context windows can =
be expensive</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c215eef367f0"></p>
<h4 local-id=3D"9722deb3c0a9" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-Rollout">Roll=
out</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"44a619de961f">
<li local-id=3D"542f30cc0e1e">
<p local-id=3D"1b6c0f4d06c5">Customer zero adoption</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9264e999d305">
<p local-id=3D"d9134785b647">LP with limited customer groups post-feb event=
</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"31e21c59fd25" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-OtherSolution=
sConsidered">Other Solutions Considered</h3>
<h4 local-id=3D"26f089403884" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-AgenticPlatfo=
rm">Agentic Platform</h4><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper im=
age-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluenc=
e-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260223-151907.png" width=3D"4=
68" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"67ed9f0186a770c7de3e69f2441c943b322c17810d56a11=
3435b0b49dd8db700" data-image-src=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki/do=
wnload/attachments/4283401991/image-20260223-151907.png?version=3D1&amp;mod=
ificationDate=3D1771860002558&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-heigh=
t=3D"848" data-width=3D"992" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linke=
d-resource-id=3D"5209260122" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked=
-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-2=
0260223-151907.png" data-base-url=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki" d=
ata-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-contain=
er-id=3D"4283401991" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"44" data-med=
ia-id=3D"dd9c57bc-4e37-4195-9308-1c8451b99c0c" data-media-type=3D"file" hei=
ght=3D"399"></span>
<h5 local-id=3D"3b523a6202cb" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-Pros.1">Pros<=
/h5>
<ul local-id=3D"739ef6a9dc33">
<li local-id=3D"1247070782ad">
<p local-id=3D"7d47a3bb2d1b">Teams building agents own no code only configu=
rations</p></li>
</ul>
<h5 local-id=3D"8e4af18a9ce0" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-Cons.1">Cons<=
/h5>
<ul local-id=3D"b3d673702564">
<li local-id=3D"d9995813f9d2">
<p local-id=3D"51f8e15123be">Heavy reliance on WIP features</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"76be432d9c45">
<p local-id=3D"e6a3a3969c00">No flexibility in agent orchestration between =
different agent implementations</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d68da0bffe71">
<p local-id=3D"bf39a4df42ee">No control levers to manage agent execution li=
fecycle</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e827c06feae0">
<p local-id=3D"00a042dedc24">Fragile execution process with many failure po=
ints</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a944f1f854eb"></p>
<h3 local-id=3D"13feb2333dd8" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-SREAgentCDD-APIs"><strong=
>APIs</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"e87918d7b107"><strong>Object Definitions</strong></p>
<h5 local-id=3D"d632dfbc-1b75-4784-b86a-ecf9f3653fa6" id=3D"id-2025/04/08-S=
REAgentCDD-Request">Request</h5>
<p local-id=3D"68f9c70fa388"><em>The agent execution request object in alig=
nment with </em><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/sea=
rch/show-me-the-run-agent-input_1dc3ad74-760f-45b8-a4fe-06895f67f453" rel=
=3D"nofollow"><em><u>AG UI=E2=80=99s RunAgentInput</u></em></a><em>. The mi=
nimum input request is as follows, for more details click the provided link=
.</em></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"e0=
4ded7b-76b1-4360-bc38-e68427ed9956" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f829e47c-1394-43ae-a2d7-09a9443d3dd6">
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"e4f36bd2-ad20-42ec-9=
258-e9cc56af1207" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"afbe50f774ec"><strong>Attribute</strong></p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"909fa74e-febb-4ca9-8=
2f2-4571d49821c7" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"59abf27c6194"><strong>Type</strong></p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"86d40292-117f-4f39-a=
992-81b18c42a3f0" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"33876a70e8df"><strong>Description</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e6a1901d-9e7f-4430-aaa8-e62c49b9901e">
