<p local-id=3D"a6e7e0f1c1e4">&nbsp;</p>
<p local-id=3D"a0b1d86c8fee"><strong>Customer Zero</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"91976fd3bbd8">Internal teams can current reach out to #help-=
ai and select <code>Agentic Platform Onboarding</code> to receive help gett=
ing their account provisioned for using the v0 implementation of SRE agent =
that currently exists. This should likely persist as the go-to mechanism fo=
r onboarding new internal users so long as the feature continues to require=
 provisioning.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-cen=
ter-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embed=
ded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20251014-215754.png" width=3D"468" loa=
ding=3D"lazy" src=3D"fdff8c7b0ec265e7ca89b081fcbf89ec3dbc85c7796ee815fa2b5d=
e2cbf63e3f" data-image-src=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki/download/=
attachments/4283401991/image-20251014-215754.png?version=3D1&amp;modificati=
onDate=3D1771860811622&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"11=
8" data-width=3D"506" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resou=
rce-id=3D"5210636297" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resour=
ce-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20251014=
-215754.png" data-base-url=3D"https://newrelic.atlassian.net/wiki" data-lin=
ked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=
=3D"4283401991" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"44" data-media-id=
=3D"7c5138ce-843b-423a-b148-1595bc4a186c" data-media-type=3D"file" height=
=3D"109"></span>
<p local-id=3D"d38c977426b3">&nbsp;</p>
<ul local-id=3D"30a3be94-2a9b-4e7f-81d1-48d153f817d8">
<li local-id=3D"62c1e105-2f6e-4e3d-bd14-a1d5dd785bd1">
<p local-id=3D"580c588bbbf8"><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" =
data-account-id=3D"5a4d7b3000a209083fb6e126" href=3D"https://newrelic.atlas=
sian.net/wiki/people/5a4d7b3000a209083fb6e126?ref=3Dconfluence" target=3D"_=
blank" data-linked-resource-id=3D"282951728" data-linked-resource-version=
=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://newr=
elic.atlassian.net/wiki">Corey Arnold</a> has kindly drafted terraform and =
scripts that quickly provision the necessary alerts concepts for quickly en=
abling existing alerts for triage by SRE agent</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c7c8a52-2107-4a45-8c5d-41d502b99595">
<p local-id=3D"c97ac6d3edaf"><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" =
data-account-id=3D"61bcd16491c049006fd3fef9" href=3D"https://newrelic.atlas=
sian.net/wiki/people/61bcd16491c049006fd3fef9?ref=3Dconfluence" target=3D"_=
blank" data-linked-resource-id=3D"2369357040" data-linked-resource-version=
=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://newr=
elic.atlassian.net/wiki">Elise Sutherland</a> has brilliantly championed th=
e actual enablement of customer zero internally.</p></li>
